2021 INDOOR SEASON

Placed ninth in the heptathlon at the Missouri Valley Conference Indoor Championships (2/26-2/28) with a score of 4,314 ... recorded a fifth-place finish in the high jump at a mark of 1.90m (6'-2.75") at the Indiana State Invitational (2/13) ... also took ninth in the shot put and 13th in the 60-meter dash at the same meet ... opened up the indoor campaign with a fifth-place finish in the long jump and ninth-place showing in the 60-meter hurdles at the Don DeNoon Dual (2/5-2/6).

2020 OUTDOOR SEASON

Canceled due to COVID-19 outbreak.

2019-20 INDOOR SEASON

Finished fifth in the heptathlon with personal-best 4,632 points to score six team points at the 2020 Missouri Valley Conference Indoor T&F Championships (2/29-3/1) ... recorded a personal-best time of 1:27.77 in the 600 meter at the 2020 Indiana University Relays (1/31-2/1) ... competed in six meets.

2019 OUTDOOR SEASON

Recorded a personal-best mark of 160'-3" in the javelin throw to finish ninth at the 2019 Missouri Valley Conference Outdoor T&F Championships (5/10-5/12) ... set a lifetime-best in the discus throw with a mark of 78'-7" at the Lenny Lyles-Clark Wood Invite (4/26-4/27) ... recorded a PR in the 1500 with a time of 4:44.53 at the Bill Cornell Spring Classic (3/22-3/23) ... competed in five meets.

2018-19 INDOOR SEASON

Set a personal-best mark in the 800 with a time of 2:10.47 at the Don DeNoon Invite (2/1-2/2) ... recorded a lifetime-best time of 53.72 in the 400 at the 2019 Indiana University Relays (1/25-1/26) ... earned three top-10 finishes in the in the first two meets of the seaosn ... comepted in four meets.

HIGH SCHOOL
